{"tid":1248622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[打氣]各位警察真係辛苦哂 唔明點解啲人要針對你哋","createTime":"2019-06-21T13:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T13:56:34.000Z","uid":242866,"like":68,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6b7829b974bdaf31d29369317078f022d3df7404","tid":1248622,"uid":242866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:36:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">收嗲啦 無撚人可憐你班垃圾啊</span><br />\n其實我真係覺得你哋班狗好撚低賤囉<br />\n除咗恥笑真係無其他感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過作為一個唔可以同你哋班狗相提並論嘅人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">都唔會可憐你哋 因為無人逼你哋做狗</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好話係我哋侮辱你<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為係你哋嘅行為根本同隻狗無分別</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾上頭講煽動幾句就咁落力做嘢<br />\n以為做緊嘅事係為自己<br />\n俾人當condom都唔知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌真係笑撚死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同我扔粒波出去 旺財幫我執翻嚟有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講乜要跟上頭order做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個唔係你哋班狗可以釋放獸性嘅理由<br />\n射高一尺射低一尺有狗糧出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你班畜牲無人性就唔好咁多籍口</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">仲想知點解我哋要圍你狗屋？因為你主人打壓自由同你班狗唔撚抵可憐囉</span></span>"},{"pid":"ea7e858bd6881a1a2ca6c332d3d38cd97c57aeea","tid":1248622,"uid":242866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:44:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f51206d0acc90702b5a1b447b63a1a3b06c481b6","tid":1248622,"uid":242866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:44:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87f6fd40ad97f25016f5f4eef66cf2d77a93c7a3","tid":1248622,"uid":242866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:47:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3dc7f3b798d44a75c61a4826608c83885a9b6a86","tid":1248622,"uid":153824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:48:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ac42a8c959bd421396d9f8628d939610308209","tid":1248622,"uid":242866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:48:44.000Z","msg":"唔係好中意上嚟攞料㗎咩"},{"pid":"f4577ce1ff82aef394b2a349bdcabd2a4fb74357","tid":1248622,"uid":242866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:49:17.000Z","msg":"而家有嘢同你講啊柒頭"},{"pid":"638827f4ad786b02bb43e7cab6d0d00f77971799","tid":1248622,"uid":242866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:50:47.000Z","msg":"咁撚鐘意上嚟攞料啊拿"},{"pid":"1c51007415e21638f558fb3f8fa604c23d38a559","tid":1248622,"uid":242866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:51:22.000Z","msg":"有無警犬？"},{"pid":"69083515fcd4b6b4d9e79abe00752a89c5d8fd4d","tid":1248622,"uid":242866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:52:12.000Z","msg":"各位推到有狗隻見到"},{"pid":"d54fdfe905c541c3388ffd8b21fcc4fb49dfbe24","tid":1248622,"uid":242866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:52:40.000Z","msg":"推到有狗隻見到"},{"pid":"47